    "name": "Egophage",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "When an intellect devourer gorges heavily on midnight milk (<i>Pathfinder Campaign Setting: Lost Cities of Golarion</i> 11), it sometimes develops increased psychic abilities, including the ability to fly, and has its stubby clawed legs stretch into tentacles. These sinister aberrations are called egophages, and delight in wearing other creatures like suits to fulfill their demented whims and schemes."
        }
    ],
